cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically with adding interpretability to pre-trained word embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with artificial intelligence and information retrieval, which makes cs.AI and cs.IR possible categories. Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category as well.
